St. Nicholas Terrace, south from about W. 133rd, to 127th Streets, showing on the right (west side) the grounds of the Convent of the Sacred Heart. Opposite same is the fenced slope
that is St. Nicholas Park.
July 1928.
Georcce L. Balgue
